    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition, and we are genuinely proud to present what is truly an exceptional example. The exterior is essentially flawless \u2014 the paint is deep, rich, and vibrant with no scratches, chips, swirl marks, or blemishes of any kind. Every panel aligns perfectly, and the chrome and trim pieces are bright and unblemished. The interior is equally impressive: the upholstery shows zero wear, all surfaces are pristine, and every control, button, and feature functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs with smooth, confident power. All mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, transmission, and cooling \u2014 are in excellent working order with no issues to report. This is a turn-key vehicle that requires absolutely nothing before driving; it is ready to go from day one and represents a rare opportunity to own a truly move-in-ready car.",
      "price": 48500.0,
