    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition, and we are committed to complete honesty with every potential buyer. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains a solid shine with only minor surface blemishes consistent with normal everyday use. You won't find any significant dents or deep scratches, though a close inspection may reveal a few small imperfections here and there. The interior is clean and comfortable, with upholstery showing light wear on the high-contact areas such as the driver's seat and door panels, but nothing excessive. Mechanically, this car has been properly maintained \u2014 the engine runs smoothly, all major systems are functioning correctly, and it drives confidently on the road. Brakes, suspension, and tires are all in serviceable condition. This is a solid, dependable vehicle for a buyer looking for reliable transportation without the premium price tag of a mint-condition car. What you see is what you get \u2014 no hidden surprises.",
      "price": 34000.0,
