    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in mint condition, and prospective buyers will find it to be an exceptional, like-new option that is rarely seen on the used market. The exterior is flawless \u2014 the paint retains a deep, showroom-quality shine with absolutely no scratches, chips, or blemishes visible anywhere on the body. All trim pieces, glass, and lights are in perfect condition. The interior is equally immaculate: every surface is clean and unmarked, the upholstery shows no wear, fading, or staining, and all electronics, controls, and features function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean and well-maintained, starting smoothly and running without any hesitation, unusual noises, or warning lights. The tires have excellent tread depth remaining, and the brakes are in top condition. Service records are available and reflect consistent, careful maintenance throughout the vehicle's life. This is a true turn-key purchase \u2014 drive it home with complete confidence.",
